<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514623>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Diagnostic external characters of Paratranes Zimmerman, 1994. A. Elytral surface and setae. B. Eyes and prothorax, ventral view. C. Head and base of rostrum, dorsal view. D. Pronotal surface. Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514623/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514631>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Habitus, lateral view. A–B. Paratranes monopticus (Pascoe, 1870). C–D. P. zimmermani sp. nov. (C. Holotype (ANIC); D. Paratype (ANIC)). A, C. Male. B, D. Female. Scale bars = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514631/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514635>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Left antenna, dorsal view. A. Paratranes monopticus (Pascoe, 1870). B. P. zimmermani sp. nov. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514629>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Habitus, dorsal view. A–B. Paratranes monopticus (Pascoe, 1870). C–D. P. zimmermani sp. nov. (C. Holotype (ANIC); D. Paratype (ANIC)). A, C. Male. B, D. Female. Scale bars = 5.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514627>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Diagnostic external characters and terminalia of Paratranes Zimmerman, 1994. A. Elytral apex. B. Right metatibia. C. Tergite VII of female. D. Tergite VIII of male. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514627/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514639>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Terminalia of Paratranes Zimmerman, 1994. A. P. monopticus (Pascoe, 1870), tergite VIII of female. B. P. monopticus, sternite VIII of female. C. P. zimmermani sp. nov., tergite VIII of female. D. P. zimmermani sp. nov., sternite VIII of female. E. P. monopticus, sternite VIII of male. F. P. zimmermani sp. nov., sternite VIII of male. G. P. monopticus, spiculum gastrale. H. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ditto. I. P. monopticus, tegmen. J. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ditto. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514639/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514643>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Penis of Paratranes Zimmerman, 1994. A. P. monopticus (Pascoe, 1870), dorsal view (Griffith Uni., Qld). B. P. monopticus, ventral view (Griffith Uni., Qld). C. P. monopticus, lateral view (Griffith Uni., Qld). D. P. zimmermani sp. nov., dorsal view (Kalbarri, WA). E. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ventral view (Kalbarri, WA). F. P. zimmermani sp. nov., lateral view (Kalbarri, WA). Scale bars = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514643/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514645>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Endophallus and apex of penis of Paratranes Zimmerman, 1994. A. P. monopticus (Pascoe, 1870), apical sclerite (Griffith Uni., Qld). B. P. monopticus, ditto (Lucindale, SA). C. P. monopticus, ditto (Deepdene, WA). D. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ditto (Kalbarri, WA). E. P. zimmermani sp. nov., apex of penis (Kalbarri, WA). F. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ditto (NSW). Scale bars = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514645/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5514649>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Female genital structures of Paratranes Zimmerman, 1994. A. P. monopticus (Pascoe, 1870), ovipositor (Homebush, NSW). B. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ditto (Wembley, WA). C. P. monopticus, spermatheca with gland (Homebush, NSW). D. P. zimmermani sp. nov., ditto (Wembley, WA). Scale bars: A–B = 0.5 mm; C–D = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5514649/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

